Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ruri-chan's clothes fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to come all the way to school to play galge during summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm afraid that if we played it at my house, my parents might find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzutsuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation has already started, so what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you guys to make me a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a role-playing fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you need it by?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline is August 28th.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I need it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, I didn't come all the way here to ask you because I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:01:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like, the best 3D angel ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ojou-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.64,0:01:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I can't believe this! Hug me, hug me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's the best! With this, tomorrow will be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, tomorrow it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guten Morgen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin', Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be heading off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O' Hello, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be back until this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamachi Kureha has turned sixteen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usami-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get these from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're home cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make all of them, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose the menu and the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to add unnecessary details.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't let it get cold. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for that, Usami-senpai, you're very good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing special. I live alone, so I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard some sort of dragging noise from that corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems that "things" do get in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean something like a poltergeist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl that was living here before was dumped by her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depressed, she knocked her head on the sink and got her hand bitten by her dog, and... and right at the very end-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop! I'm terrible with scary stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The television just turns itself on sometimes, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt you, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, since we're all excited, it is time to open the long-awaited presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clap, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is sort of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rim's curvature is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge is stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nothing wrong with either temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dazzle of the lenses and the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pair of glasses has strong exorcising powers. It's able to exorcise any spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If you have this, there is nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving me these glasses. This is now the best present.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kureha-chan, happy birthday."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something along those lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kya, Konoe-senpai! {chenpai?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usami-senpai, did you make this yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I am a textile arts club member, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will sleep with Konoe-senpai from tonight onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's time for the second part of your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it away, Usami-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Are we really doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Script by Narumi Nakuru, "Memories of Class" version.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jirou-kin and Barusu, A Late Summer Night's Memories."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the show begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barusu. Oh, how hard it is to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you are here in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jirou-kin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, hug me tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barusu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this is our last night together. My love for you is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nakuru. We're overdoing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please bear with it for now. After all, this is Kureha-chan's birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jirou-kin, I too, want to make you and your glasses my love forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the two lovers made a promise with a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Usami-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by Barusu and Jirou-kin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that we're portraying Idiot-Chicken and Subaru here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, please. {boring show - editor agrees.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, time for the third stage of your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will move to the next venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next venue? {she looks miserable}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kya, Konoe-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the next venue that we mentioned, Maid Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two more years to go before you can watch 18+ hentai, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the two of you know it was my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nakuru. Why here of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milady has reserved this place for the day. Please have as much fun as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Usagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you in a maid's outfit one more time, my little rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me "Usagi-chan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please go ahead, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then everyone, shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From me to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan! {FFFF THIS MAYO EP IS A FILLER}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gazing sheep! {THE DOLLS NAME}{OK}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Konoe-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To meet you with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wishes will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the best present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we go somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From me to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From me to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly remembered my eighth birthday... {8 years ago.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Daddy. I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, Ku-re-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your present. Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I will name this bear, Bro-Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best present ever, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother bought my present with all of the money from his savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a wonderful brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Idiot-Chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice memory, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh.{make this the release pic with title: TL was tired hes taking a break (I wear glasses, I have black hair, I like cup Ramen)}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, my type is curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lovely kiss for you, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Mayo Chiki}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to blow you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't wear panties as long as I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:13:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to play a game like this where I was the main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, I knew people who could make this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you forced them into making it through some evil scheme of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, why is that Idiot-Chicken is hardly wearing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be precise, he is wearing underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my brother, so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have no fear, the glasses are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cats ears and striped thigh-high socks, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses and garter belt, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person does look like pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For him to appear in a game hardly wearing anything, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about being young and youthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not a cycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jirou's only wearing his boxers and chasing his sister inside a convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a development!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what is what anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to take me on? You're sixteen years too early kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to let him win once, at least just in a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama, let me have one more go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the best birthday I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That playground...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, during my tenth birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother's waiting for us, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still remember his face when he came to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jirou-kun is a good brother, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my twelfth birthday...{honestly what a boring show}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We played video games the entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my thirteenth, we brought ice-cream at a dairy farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fourteenth birthday was all about fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to remember all of your birthdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is, today is... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The twenty-eighth of August.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurose says he got some tickets to a live show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we're so lucky. That's a platinum ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, sis! I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't this t-shirt great?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was one of the last ones they had. I'm going to take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean! You forgot your sister's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kureha. It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! You idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped since Jirou-kun forgot about his only sister's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year, my mother is abroad, so she's not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had everyone celebrate it with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop being Jirou-kun's little sister and become my little sister instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Jirou that doesn't care about his sister's feelings has no right to be a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ojou-sama, isn't there something called a 'mistake'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you become his little sister if you want defend him this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to, then I'd rather be his little brother than his little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, it was my brother who came to my middle school opening ceremony in the place of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also said, "It suits you very nicely" when I wore my high school uniform for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, he's my partner when I train. {This HAS TO BE THE BLOG POST PIC}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always treated me with kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should become his strength. After all, I'm already sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why, even if he forgot my birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always pays attention to me all the other times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have the rest of the presents delivered later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Jirou-kun remembered his sister's birthday this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that it'll all be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san, can it be? Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, a big stuffed doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cute, white doggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Kureha, but that's a polar bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Thank you, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised myself after seeing Kureha so sad that I would never make the same mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, sorry about last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san, this just might be the happiest birthday ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say Nii-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel like hugging you all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I hug you for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It still came down to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, HAPPY BIRTHDAY, MY SISTER!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Subterranean Rabbit"? What's with this weird title?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a present for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something way shadier than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Suzutsuki Kanade, like hell I'm going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me. There's only enough space for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, what an unsightly heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game over, Usagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzutsuki Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ojou-sama, may I hug you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I want to plant this face of mine onto your chest and never move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, I also want to kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smell the tantalizing perfume of your ebony hair forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it in much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, are you're also taken in by this side of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who hears that will get taken in as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spell of the demon, the calling of magic, the cursed word.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.24,0:24:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of Mayo Chiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 11th Story, Nyu.
